rows.label: qev092503_MSG0001
rows.name: I gotta say, it looked pretty fun. How did it feel?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092503_MSG0002
rows.name:
Any problems?
Tell me everything down to the tiniest detail. I need it ALL![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092503_SEL0011
rows.name: Tell them that you flew with no problems.

rows.label: qev092503_SEL0021
rows.name: Say it's a bit difficult to control...

rows.label: qev092503_MSG0003
rows.name:
I felt like I was flying myself,
and that's just from watching you down here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092503_MSG0004
rows.name: You could go anywhere with that Skell![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092503_MSG0005
rows.name:
Well, it was a bit difficult to control myself, too, watching you
wobble all over the place after I worked all night![ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092503_MSG0006
rows.name: ...Uh, I mean, that's good feedback, thanks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092503_MSG0007
rows.name: You probably just need a little time to get used to flying.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092503_MSG0008
rows.name:
Well in any case, you make it back to New LA
in one piece and we'll call this a success.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092503_MSG0009
rows.name: Just make sure to stay focused, okay?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev092503_MSG0010
rows.name: I know you'll make it home without a scratch.[ST:wait ]
